Creative Commons Legal Code

CC0 1.0 Universal

The learnings in this repository are dedicated to the public domain under the
Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication.

To the extent possible under law, contributors to komi-pool have waived all
copyright and related or neighboring rights to the learning content contributed
here. You can copy, modify, distribute, and use the learnings, even for commercial
purposes, all without asking permission.

By contributing, you affirm that the content is general and non-identifying, and
that you have the right to dedicate it to the public domain.

